A similar expansion was first derived in (and later rederived in
many papers) for the projection onto the hyperplane where particles have the
same usual time. The infinite series of quasipot  for the light-cone
potential , suggests that the light-cone wave function be expanded in orders
of the strength of the BS potential . Our task is to construct gauge
invariant currents in terms of these light-cone wave functions.

